Source.Name: seahorse
Source.Summary: GNOME encryption key and password manager
Source.Description: Seahorse is a GNOME application for managing encryption keys and passwords in the GnomeKeyring. There's also a collection of plugins that integrate seahorse with nautilus, gedit and other places for encryption, decryption and other operations.
